457
00:30:30,300 --> 00:30:31,176
Yes, I have.

458
00:30:31,941 --> 00:30:33,261
I am very satisfied.

459
00:30:33,661 --> 00:30:35,181
Can you really

460
00:30:35,421 --> 00:30:37,380
